  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject, ResourceUsage
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GaScenarioImpl

    public class ResourceUsageImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements ResourceUsage
    An implementation of the model object 'Resource Usage'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Exec Time
    • Allocated Memory
    • Used Memory
    • Power Peak
    • Energy
    • Base Named Element
    • Sub Usage
    • Used Resources
    • Msg Size
